	This is a video of a simulation I made with python and matplotlib.  It is the standard <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inverted_pendulum">Inverted Pendulum</a> control problem, I implemented an <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linear-quadratic_regulator">LQR Contoller</a> in <a href="http://sourceforge.net/apps/mediawiki/python-control/index.php?title=Main_Page">python-control</a> for stabilization.  To bring the pendulum from the down position to upright, I used an energy based controller. 

